  "instructions": [
    "Shred the napa cabbage into thin strips using a knife or mandoline and place in a large bowl.",
    "Dice the cucumber, red bell pepper, and halve the cherry tomatoes, then add them to the cabbage.",
    "Slice the Kalamata olives and crumble the feta cheese, then combine all vegetables in the bowl.",
    "In a small bowl whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, dried oregano, salt, and pepper to make the dressing.",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss gently until all ingredients are evenly coated.",
    "Sprinkle toasted pine nuts on top for added crunch.",
    "Let the salad rest for 5 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Divide the salad into four portions and serve immediately."
  ],
